Reference 
cloneElement(element, props, ...children) 
Call cloneElement to create a React element based on the element, but with different props and children:
import { cloneElement } from 'react';
// ...
const clonedElement = cloneElement(
<Row title="Cabbage">
Hello
</Row>,
{ isHighlighted: true },
'Goodbye'
